Build local demand generation programs to drive sales, Upsell and High Performance product initiativesTrade Marketing:-
Support the management of distributor relationships within channel along with RSM/NAM's-
Develop and implement trade marketing programs targeting distributors and retailers-
Develop incentive programs with organized retail and SMB retail channel by countryCategory Management :-
