Ensure timely and accurate reporting of marketing budget spend and allocation to Regional Marketing ManagerAgency Management:-
Manage relevant agency relationships-
Maximize ROI of marketing spend at an agency level-
Write and communicate project briefs to agenciesTrade Shows / Exhibitions-
Be responsible for managing local trade shows & exhibitions-
Support local Retailer & Distributor trade shows & conferencesPR-
Work with RMM and the local agencies to execute Brand messaging. Liaise with EMEA/ Regional PR team and Regional product managers to develop PR programs that will build SanDisk brand awareness & generate interest in the SanDisk product portfolio.-
Grow social media visibility to promote and support brand and product messaging.Marketing Communications- Ensure brand compliance within MEA Regional Marketing & Product marketing teams, Distributors and Retail partners.- Work with Product & channel marketing to ensure effective availability & delivery of localized MarComs materials-
